name: stakefish
description:
stakefish is the leading validator for Proof of Stake blockchains. Delegate to us, stake with us. We know staking.

Pool your digital assets with stake.fish and watch them grow. Our top-notch security and white-glove support protects you from risk while granting peace of mind.

Running a validator requires significant amounts of expertise, time, and capital. While potentially lucrative, staking tokens exposes validators to security risks and technical difficulties.
